# All Star Cleaning — Windsurf Rules

Astro 6.3 + Cloudflare Pages marketing site. 1000+ static pages, bilingual EN/FR. Full context in `AGENTS.md`, `DESIGN.md`, `PRODUCT.md`.

## Non-negotiable conventions

- **Path alias**: `@/*` → `src/*`. Never use `../` chains.
- **Layouts**: Use `PageLayout.astro` for all content pages. Prop is `schema` (singular) — never `schemas`.
- **JSON-LD**: Use generators from `src/seo/` only. Never hand-write structured data.
- **Tailwind tokens**: CSS vars from `src/styles/global.css`. Never hardcode hex. `--tw-*` vars are renamed to `--c-*` in production — never reference them directly.
- **i18n**: Every string has EN + FR. Use `useTranslations(locale)` for common UI strings, `isFr` boolean for page-specific text.
- **Static only**: No backend, no DB, no SSR. Forms via Web3Forms only.

## Design hard rules (see DESIGN.md for full system)

- No pure `#000` / `#fff` for large areas
- No gradient text (`background-clip: text` + gradient)
- No decorative side-stripe borders (> 1px border-left/right as accent)
- No nested cards
- 44×44px minimum touch targets
- Always add hover, focus, active states to interactive elements

## Extending the project

- **New location**: append to `src/data/locations.ts` → 900 programmatic pages auto-generate
- **New service**: create `src/content/services/{slug}.json`, add to `src/data/services.ts`
- **New page**: wrap in `PageLayout.astro`, pass `schema` array from `src/seo/` generators

## Commands

```bash
npm run dev       # http://localhost:4321
npm run build     # ./dist/
npm run typecheck # astro check (only lint available)
```
